></blockquote>oo (good)同 ee (see) 呢兩個vowel既特性係會偏向&quot;假&quot;既音質<br />\n所以歌曲遇到呢兩個vowel係高音又想佢有個&quot;真&quot;的既音質就會做的所謂vowel modification:<br />\noo 轉去 ou (book) 既方向 <br />\nee 轉去 ih (sit) 既方向, 甚至去到eh, 英文歌如果你細心留意好多人高音ee其實係唱緊eh<br />\n<br />\nTLDR: 個口向下開多的就會自然做到呢個modification <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>同埋你講嘅ou 同埋 ih音<br />\n有無字例講嚟聽吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上面有寫, 是book同sit<br />\n廣東話係難的, 要做到轉得黎仲聽到你隻字怪左<br />\n同埋高音除左個vowel要用得岩, 閉合同氣個平衡都要做得好先上到"},{"pid":"e44ba4aec0dac145b9d3b4a14b0961e939dd8087","tid":998040,"uid":195396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T12:17:12.000Z","msg":"再問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想唱到張宇嗰種厚度又要有佢個range可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢啲歌個range係上假音又奇怪真音又好易唱到無氣嗰啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b44c01486aae2c5cb8552eb43170ed068d4b5e34","tid":998040,"uid":37795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e44ba4aec0dac145b9d3b4a14b0961e939dd8087","tid":998040,"uid":195396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T12:17:12.000Z","msg":"再問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想唱到張宇嗰種厚度又要有佢個range可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢啲歌個range係上假音又奇怪真音又好易唱到無氣嗰啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T14:53:44.000Z","msg":"聽你咁講你似係用錯力上高音，出去搵個mix voice老師學好的，自己練好易練錯整傷埋自己"},{"pid":"37c0a1b3614f889c9c588150cf4483953b909c41","tid":998040,"uid":195396,"like":0,"dislike":1,